<div class='mainBanner row'>

    <div class='left col-lg-5'>
      <div class='col-lg-4 col-md-5 col-sm-3 col-xs-3'></div>
      <div class='col-lg-8 col-md-7 col-sm-7 col-xs-7'>
      <ul class='homeDescription'>
        <li>Post your projects and connect with people to work on them.</li>
        <li>Offer your skills to others to help them complete their projects.</li>
        <li>Be a part of something innovative.</li>
      </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='right col-lg-7'>
      <ul class='pictures row'>
        <li class='col-lg-12'><img src='/banner1.png' ></li>
        <li class='col-lg-12'><img src='/banner2.png' ></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>


  <div class='col-lg-12'>
    <div class='buttons'>
      <%= link_to 'Browse Open Projects', projects_path %>
    </div>
    <div class='signUp'>
      <p>Or <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_path %> to begin posting!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class='mainBody row'>
  <div class='col-lg-1 col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2'></div>
  <div class='left why col-lg-5 col-md-9 col-sm-8 col-xs-8'>
    <h3>Why Collaborate?</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>You need help on that project you working on, be it a side project or something you have always wanted to do.</li>
      <li>You have a special skill, and you want to help others.</li>
      <li>You want to learn a new skill by working with someone else, amateur or professional.</li>
      <li>You want to experience or create something new.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class='col-lg-1 col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-2'></div>
  <div class='right what col-lg-5 col-md-9 col-sm-8 col-xs-8'>
    <h3>What Can I Collaborate On?</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>Anything!</li>
      <li>Write a work of fiction.</li>
      <li>Work on a film.</li>
      <li>Go on a photography expedition.</li>
      <li>Learn to code with someone, and build an app.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

